title_en: 1931 Willie Haney Letters, Pt. 04 [the rabbit, alligator, and rattle snake or king snake]
comment: "The Rabbit + Aligator + Rattle snake or King snake. The Rabbit is seeking to get wisdom from the head people and the head people had send the Rabbit to aligator to bring dead and Rabbit killed and to snake also."
